{
  "stem": "1929.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was very fortunate because a lot of the-- a lot of the prisoners of war, even the ones that were treated in the hospital, they would be officially discharged.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, they would be machine gunned because they were no longer-- they were no longer prisoners of war, so they had nothing to protect them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the end, they knew, yeah, they knew he was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And wherever there was no Nazi there present, they were really very human towards him and did their best for him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When he came back into the ghetto, you know, we didn't know if he was coming back, and there was, of course, my father, and mother, and sister were, we were just so thrilled to see him back.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was a big celebration.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he-- because he was a prisoner of war and he needed medical attention, he was able to go out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had permission to go outside the ghetto for treatment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he made-- he was able to make contact outside of the ghetto, which was enormously helpful later on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was able to establish contact with his former business partners, things like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, I need a rest.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
